This is a demo Rails 3 app that uses Solr/Sunspot for testing in Tddium.

It uses the sunspot_test gem, and it's largely based on example code written by
Collective Idea in their great explanation described in more detail here:

http://collectiveidea.com/blog/archives/2011/03/08/full-text-searching-with-solr-and-sunspot/

and 

https://github.com/collectiveidea/sunspot_test
